{"id": "1500823524145762415", "channel_id": "1500823524145762415", "author_id": "850363603018186802", "author_name": "tnimreppep", "content": "With the new Traphase update, you are now required to play 150 cards to earn 250 Silver and 5 Pure Cores. In this short guide, I’ll show you the quickest way (in my opinion) to hit that 150-card mark.", "timestamp": "2026-05-04T11:36:52.109000+00:00", "thread_id": "1500823524145762415", "reactions": [{"emoji": "gogogo", "emoji_id": "1356053074560422118", "count": 3}, {"emoji": "huh1", "emoji_id": "1356053088552747141", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "🫃", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1500823524372123699", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-05-04-18-20-35-381_com.android.chrome.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 619334, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1500823524145762415/1500823524372123699/Screenshot_2026-05-04-18-20-35-381_com.android.chrome.png?ex=69f9d654&is=69f884d4&hm=7eef427a0ef66af647a4204b639cb6aa1725c6e56a57bda3932cca28add4be61&"}]}
{"id": "1500828657982246963", "channel_id": "1500823524145762415", "author_id": "850363603018186802", "author_name": "tnimreppep", "content": "The F2P Strategy (Low Budget)\nBest for: New players or those saving resources.\nCore Team: Uhvash, Casiah, Alva and 1 charcter who has good Aliemus gain(Leigh or Karen)\nHow it works: This deck focuses on \"Cycle\" cards. You want to spam 0-cost or 1-cost cards to inflate your cards played number. You can spam Alva's Insight Strike or Karen's cards and cycle back to it for more cards played. Alva costs you 1 arith for 4 cards played (with Song of the Bound WOD) while karen has 2 cards that can be used 3 times and an 0 arith card. Uhvash has a card that reduces its arith cost for every card used so make sure to utilize it\nYour hands can be cycled with the help of Cassiah's card or Happy Magic Show\nKey Cards:\nAll of the WODs are mandatory: Song Of The Bound(Alva)=Epiphany(Cassiah)>Happy Magic Show=Emerge(can be equipped ASAP or on whoever has their Exalt ready)", "timestamp": "2026-05-04T11:57:16.111000+00:00", "thread_id": "1500823524145762415", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-04T12:12:56.490000+00:00", "attachments": [{"id": "1500828657646829670", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-05-04-18-15-06-405_com.qookkagames.z1.qooapp.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1519782, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1500823524145762415/1500828657646829670/Screenshot_2026-05-04-18-15-06-405_com.qookkagames.z1.qooapp.png?ex=69f9db1c&is=69f8899c&hm=19a591530022fc3903fff302e13b5ae4a93e8f743c5838d2c6f7418567d4dc64&"}]}
{"id": "1500828998802997278", "channel_id": "1500823524145762415", "author_id": "850363603018186802", "author_name": "tnimreppep", "content": "If you want to both win and reach 150 cards fast you can use Hameln:\nHe provides your team with alot of card draw with his crazy Aliemus gain + he does damage", "timestamp": "2026-05-04T11:58:37.369000+00:00", "thread_id": "1500823524145762415", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-04T12:24:45.096000+00:00", "attachments": [{"id": "1500828998207279197", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-05-04-18-15-14-718_com.qookkagames.z1.qooapp.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1607594, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1500823524145762415/1500828998207279197/Screenshot_2026-05-04-18-15-14-718_com.qookkagames.z1.qooapp.png?ex=69f9db6d&is=69f889ed&hm=e029ab360d4b25d7213e55f873bdad04fa830937d1feabc1c02ced932d3e203c&"}]}
